OL,3,CConcerns island air fare rises could
OL,4,Cthreaten tourism economy
OL,6,FAir fare rises on flights to Alderney
OL,7,Fwill threaten tourism, the economy,
OL,8,Fand the viability of the Bailiwick,
OL,9,Faccording to islanders.
OL,11,FThe cost of a ticket is set to rise by
OL,12,Faround #25 to #30 from January 2025.
OL,14,FIt's the result of a States of
OL,15,FGuernsey decision to cut taxpayer
OL,16,Fspending on flights to the island.
OL,18,FCurrently, the government is committed
OL,19,Fto a subsidy on flights to Alderney of
OL,20,F#2 million for 2024.
