OL,3,CConcerns island air fare rises could
OL,4,Cthreaten tourism economy
OL,6,FHowever, the Policy & Resources
OL,7,FCommittee (P&R) announced on Thursday
OL,8,F14 November an expected #600,000
OL,9,Foverspend.
OL,11,FTo combat this overspend, P&R has
OL,12,Fimplemented an immediate #5 increase
OL,13,Fto prices and a reduction of the
OL,14,Fsubsidy to #1.5 million for 2025.
OL,16,FWhilst there are reassurances that
OL,17,FGuernsey-Alderney route will be
OL,18,Fprotected, the Southampton service
OL,19,Fwill be hit most significantly; a
OL,20,Freturn flight could cost as much as
OL,21,F#400.
