OL,3,CConcerns island air fare rises could
OL,4,Cthreaten tourism economy
OL,6,FThis compares, however, favourably to
OL,7,Fprices for return trips of similar
OL,8,Flengths:
OL,10,FThere are concerns that Alderney's
OL,11,Fgovernment was not consulted on the
OL,12,Fchange.
OL,14,FFurther, people who depend on the
OL,15,Fservice have shared their
OL,16,Ffrustrations, with some regular fliers
OL,17,Fsuggesting the Bailiwick is no longer
OL,18,Ffunctional.
