OL,3,CConcerns island air fare rises could
OL,4,Cthreaten tourism economy
OL,6,FVicky Chandler, Alderney Week leader,
OL,7,Fworries the prices will jeopardise the
OL,8,Fbiggest tourist event in the calendar,
OL,9,Fwith ramifications for the island's
OL,10,Feconomy.
OL,12,FShe says: "If people aren't coming to
OL,13,FAlderney Week, people are not going to
OL,14,Fbe spending in the shops (and) they're
OL,15,Fnot going to be spending in the
OL,16,Frestaurants.
OL,18,F"It's going to have a huge knock-on
OL,19,Feffect for everybody."
